# 🏷️ Branding

Contains core brand assets that define the project's identity and appearance.

## Assets

- `logos/` — Various sizes and formats of official logos
- `icons/` — Custom or selected icon sets
- `style-guide.pdf` — PDF of the branding rules (colors, spacing, usage)

> 🎨 Follow this to avoid off-brand horrors.

